lead_paragraph: The executions of two Kuwaitis and five foreigners were the first in the country in over three years and reflected a wider return to the death penalty in the region.

headline.main: Kuwait Hangs 7 Convicts, Including a Prince
headline.print_headline: Prince and 6 More Convicts Are Executed in Kuwait
